title: IoT in Health Podcast S.1 Ep.4 iBoss
description:
On this episode of the monthly IoT in Health Podcast, Ken Briodagh, editorial director at IoT Evolution Health (iotevolutionhealth.com), sits down with Paul Martini, CEO, iBoss Network Security (iboss.com), to talk about Secure Cloud Connectivity, Patient privacy and regulatory compliance.

Register now for the upcoming IoT Evolution Health Conference (www.iotevolutionhealth.com/conference), coming up January 29 to February 1 in Ft. Lauderdale, Florida.

Please check out "IoT Time: Evolving Trends in the Internet of Things," a book by Ken Briodagh about the ongoing influences shaping the IoT. To get a digital copy, download it here for free (www.iotevolutionworld.com/iot-ebook.aspx). A print edition is also available on Amazon for $14.99.

To become a sponsor of IoT in Health, please email kbriodagh@tmcnet.com or tweet @KenBriodagh.
